1. *Pravo* je da se odluči ono što je najbolje za sve. (The right is to decide what is best for everyone.) 

2. Ona je imala ispravno *pravo* da odluči. (She had the right to decide correctly.) 

3. Oni su u potpunosti iskoristili svoje *pravo* da glasaju. (They fully exercised their right to vote.) 

4. Oni su primenili svoje *pravo* da se zaštite. (They applied their right to protect themselves.)

5. *Pravo* na jednakost je zagarantovano ukoliko se poštuju zakoni. (The right to equality is guaranteed as long as the laws are respected.)